info.title: Noggin Connect API
info.description:
The Noggin Connect API provides an interface for interacting with data in the Noggin platform. The endpoints described in this documentation are specific to this instance of the platform.

# Authentication

<!-- ReDoc-Inject: <security-definitions> -->

get.summary: Fetch any object by its tip
get.description: Returns a single object by its tip

parameters.name: tip
parameters.description: The tip of the object to retrieve

parameters.name: branch
parameters.description: The branch to retrieve the object from

parameters.name: embedSystem
parameters.description: Whether or not to embed system objects inline, such as assignments and addresses

parameters.name: allFields
parameters.description: Whether or not to send all fields in the response

200.description: The object was successfully retrieved. It is important to note that as this end point can return any object, schemas of internal platform objects may change without notice.

403.description: Retrieving this object is not permitted

get.summary: Fetch any object version by its sid
get.description: Returns a single object by its sid

parameters.name: sid
parameters.description: The sid of the object to retrieve

parameters.name: embedSystem
parameters.description: Whether or not to embed system objects inline, such as assignments and addresses

parameters.name: allFields
parameters.description: Whether or not to send all fields in the response

200.description: The object version was successfully retrieved.  It is important to note that as this end point can return any object, schemas of internal platform objects may change without notce.

403.description: Retrieving this object version is not permitted

get.summary: Fetch Shift
get.description: Returns a single shift object by its tip

parameters.name: tip
parameters.description: The tip of the shift to retrieve

200.description: The shift is successfully retrieved. It is important to note that this end point can return only shift object.

403.description: Retrieving this shift object is not permitted

post.summary: Filter Shifts

403.description: Executing the query is not permitted

500.description: The query failed due to some unspecified reason

504.description: The query timed out and needs optimizing

post.summary: Invite an existing contact to be a user

profiles.description: The profiles to assign to the invited users

lang.description: The language to assign to the invited users

identityProvider.description: The tip of the identity provider to assign to the invited users

403.description: Inviting the contacts is not permitted

patch.summary: Update a user

email.description: The email address/identifier of the user to update

profiles.description: The profiles to set for the user

identityProvider.description: The tip of the identity provider to set for the user

idpNameId.description: The identifier that will be associated with the user, instead of the email address, for use with SSO identity providers

contact.description: The tip of the contact to set for the user

status.description: The status to set for the user

newEmail.description: The email address to change the user to

403.description: Updating users is not permitted

delete.summary: Deprovision user

email.description: The email address of the user to deprovision

403.description: Deprovisioning users is not permitted

post.summary: Execute a query
post.description: Note: For REST API requests that need pagination, use after as a property instead of a variable. The old method to use it as a variable will be deprecated soon.

parameters.name: tip
parameters.description: The tip of the query filter to execute

attributes.description: The attributes to return for each data point

lang.description: The list of language preferences to return the results in

field.description: The field key to sort on

403.description: Executing the query is not permitted

500.description: The query failed due to some unspecified reason

504.description: The query timed out and needs optimizing

post.summary: Send location

createdAt.description: The optional point in time of the location

geoJson.description: The GeoJSON point of the location

coordinates.description: An array containing the longitude and latitude

items.description: Longitude and latitude of the GeoJSON point

tip.description: The tip details for which locations needs to capture

404.description: The requested url was not found

500.description: The operation failed due to some unspecified reason

post.summary: Geocode an given address

suggestion.description: The text whose address should be geocoded

magicKey.description: An ID attribute value that, along with the text attribute, links a suggestion to an address or place

500.description: The operation failed due to some unspecified reason

post.summary: Send sms to given phone number

mobile.description: Mobile number to which sms needs to be sent

smsTemplate.description: Template containing the message to be sent to given mobile number

400.description: Invalid payload to twilio service

500.description: The operation failed due to some unspecified reason
